tic family.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isfahan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.705922310081635e-30, \"text\": \"Isfahan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isfahan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isfahan\"}, {\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999553098350689, \"rank\": 4.428809315228889e-05, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fasihi\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"an athletic family\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father was a volleyball player, and her brother a swimming and diving champion.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her father\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"a volleyball player\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"her brother\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimming and diving champion\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Before I got married, my father attended all my training sessions,\\\" she recalls.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my father\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"all my training sessions\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mother also attended all my competitions.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My mother\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"all my competitions\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without their support, I could not have succeeded.\\\"\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\